      <title>陆军为与特朗普团队对峙的阿灵顿公墓工作人员辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/army-defends-cemetery-staffer-who-confronted-trump-s-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国陆军为一名在参观阿灵顿国家公墓期间与唐纳德·特朗普竞选团队发生冲突的工作人员辩护，称她被“突然推到一边”，然后在事件发生后遭到“不公平的攻击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/army-defends-cemetery-staffer-who-confronted-trump-s-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊与沙特协调避免红海油轮灾难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/greece-saudi-arabia-coordinate-to-avert-oil-tanker-disaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，希腊正在牵头清空并拖走上周在红海遭到袭击的一艘油轮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/greece-saudi-arabia-coordinate-to-avert-oil-tanker-disaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
